sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Writer
    participant Web as Web App
    participant API as Node API
    participant AIS as AI Service
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant RT as Realtime Hub

    Writer->>Web: Select text and request rewrite
    Web->>API: POST /ai-operations<br/>feature + selection + version
    API->>AIS: Validate role, scope context,<br/>create queued interaction
    AIS-->>API: interactionId + queued status
    API-->>Web: 202 Accepted

    AIS->>LLM: Submit scoped prompt<br/>with template version
    LLM-->>AIS: Suggested text
    AIS->>AIS: Persist completed result<br/>and requestedVersion
    AIS->>RT: Emit ai.completed
    RT-->>Web: Push completed interaction
    Web-->>Writer: Show proposal in AI panel

    alt User applies while document version is unchanged
        Writer->>Web: Apply suggestion
        Web->>API: POST /ai-interactions/:id/apply
        API->>AIS: Verify suggestion is not stale
        AIS->>API: Updated content + new version
        API->>RT: Broadcast document.updated
        RT-->>Web: Push updated document
        Web-->>Writer: Show saved content and history
    else Document changed before apply
        Writer->>Web: Apply stale suggestion
        Web->>API: POST /ai-interactions/:id/apply
        API-->>Web: 409 AI_CONTEXT_STALE
        Web-->>Writer: Prompt reload or fresh AI request
    end
